{"tid":1935795,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Zm 130蚊報到","createTime":"2020-03-20T20:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T08:09:35.000Z","uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a6028d8d79263a166e586a455f86cb7eddb6f8","tid":1935795,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T20:30:34.000Z","msg":"呢排嗰個work from home又係屋企上堂<br />\nZoom咁多人用<br />\n淨係廣告都賺死<br />\n依家130蚊抵玩到喊<br />\n逆市勁升既Zoom video stock可以幫呢度既手足止血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98289c12f6c0782b5e5176751bb58c9932e751d","tid":1935795,"uid":138809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T20:32:54.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"58275a3f2f8c8ce12093a558f6116d3247d34728","tid":1935795,"uid":192798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1a6028d8d79263a166e586a455f86cb7eddb6f8","tid":1935795,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T20:30:34.000Z","msg":"呢排嗰個work from home又係屋企上堂<br />\nZoom咁多人用<br />\n淨係廣告都賺死<br />\n依家130蚊抵玩到喊<br />\n逆市勁升既Zoom video stock可以幫呢度既手足止血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200407/5D6H5PRZAWDIRH3SKJGUSTVCBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200407%2F5D6H5PRZAWDIRH3SKJGUSTVCBA%2F&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXBw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=9980d07c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200407%2F5D6H5PRZAWDIRH3SKJGUSTVCBA%2F&h=22be9f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200407/5D6H5PRZAWDIRH3SKJGUSTVCBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n//武漢肺炎全球大爆發，為減少接觸，不少人在家工作，研發中心設在中國的視像通訊軟件ZOOM大行其道。不過，Zoom被揭發有嚴重安全漏洞，將用戶資料及會議內容都傳到中國，Zoom創辦人袁征隨後承認問題，並公開道歉。不過，台灣行政院今日發出通函，禁止政府機構使用有安全疑慮的產品，包括Zoom，優先使用台灣產品或已獲認證的產品。<br />\n<br />\n行政院資通安全處（以下簡稱「資安處」）今日表示，台灣去年已實施《資通安全管理法》，各政府部門在資訊傳遞及資訊安全安防護上，都要依照相關規定處理、落實，以維護國家安全。資安處指，在各政府機構的系統中，不應使用有安全疑慮的產品，如果需要使用，也應以台灣產品及與政府有共同供應契約的產品優先。<br />\n<br />\n行政院發言人谷辣斯．尤達卡（Kolas Yotaka）昨曾表示，目前行政院進行視像會議，沒有使用Zoom這個軟件，資安處初步統計，各部會也沒有使用。台灣外交部表示，因為Zoom是中國產品，該部沒有使用。<br />\n<br />\n行政院資安處進一步表示，如果情況特殊或需要與國際交流，必須使用非台灣製的視像訊訊軟體，可使用主要國際服務商的軟件。台灣教育部則推薦學校使用Google Meet、Microsoft Teams等軟件，作為向在家學生授課的軟件。//"},{"pid":"ef3b553b1d1baaf78bc1ae5d8930fb20b3cd596a","tid":1935795,"uid":94151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:16:30.000Z","msg":"買大陸股 抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1224e6b38eba458572b2331c068ac814523d0a","tid":1935795,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3b553b1d1baaf78bc1ae5d8930fb20b3cd596a","tid":1935795,"uid":94151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:16:30.000Z","msg":"買大陸股 抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T08:09:35.000Z","msg":"150蚊放左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}